article.description: — DeVante' Jones scored 19 points as Coastal Carolina topped NC Central 78-71 on Monday night.
article.headline: Jones leads Coastal Carolina past NC Central 78-71
article.linkText: Jones leads Coastal Carolina past NC Central 78-71
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — DeVante' Jones scored 19 points as Coastal Carolina topped NC Central 78-71 on Monday night. Tyrik Dixon and Deanthony Tipler added 16 points each, and Ebrima Dibba had 10 points and seven assists for Coastal Carolina (3-0). C.J. Keyser had 19 points for the Eagles (1-2). Jahnathan Maxwell added 13 points, and Deven Palmer had 10 points and six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
